c68fc2c6-192f-489f-a693-3c92d8cb7bb2.title: Survival Expert
c68fc2c6-192f-489f-a693-3c92d8cb7bb2.text:
Hello there, newcomer. My name is Brynna. My job is
to teach you a few survival tips and tricks. First off
we're going to start with the most basic survival skill of
all: making a fire.

91d13925-4e8b-46ea-a35b-c422146d23d2.title: Survival Expert
91d13925-4e8b-46ea-a35b-c422146d23d2.text:
Well done! Next we need to get some food in our
bellies. We'll need something to cook. There are shrimp
in the pond there, so let's catch and cook some.

ff75394a-d556-44c2-8529-663a67f7cb9a.title: Survival Expert
ff75394a-d556-44c2-8529-663a67f7cb9a.text:
Well done! You can now move on to the next instructor.
Go through the gate and follow the path.

55523450-848f-413b-8237-fe450c3a95b8.title: What would you like to hear more about?

16f60aa1-7275-4bd1-bee5-fd46156e04c0.title: Survival Expert
16f60aa1-7275-4bd1-bee5-fd46156e04c0.text:
Woodcutting, eh? Don't worry, newcomer, it's really
very easy. Simply equip your axe and click on a
nearby tree and chop away.

ee17eeba-0428-496c-a7b8-ed2266444465.title: Survival Expert
ee17eeba-0428-496c-a7b8-ed2266444465.text:
As you explore the mainland you will discover many
different kinds of trees that will require different levels
of Woodcutting ability to chop down.

249e10ce-f846-42e0-b68b-66b88f9ee955.title: Survival Expert
249e10ce-f846-42e0-b68b-66b88f9ee955.text:
Logs are not only useful for making fires. Many
archers use the skill known as Fletching to craft their
own bows and arrows from trees.

5377f006-be56-4b2c-99ee-cecdb2db4a08.title: Survival Expert
5377f006-be56-4b2c-99ee-cecdb2db4a08.text:
Certainly, newcomer. When you have logs simply use
your tinderbox on them. If successful, you will start a
fire.

9b602f9b-1572-4d75-8182-cfe9f682ba51.title: Survival Expert
9b602f9b-1572-4d75-8182-cfe9f682ba51.text:
A tinderbox is always a useful item to keep around!
Was there anything else you wished to hear again?

3f78aa4d-d1a1-461b-b40b-818ef5e602be.title: Survival Expert
3f78aa4d-d1a1-461b-b40b-818ef5e602be.text:
Ah yes. Fishing! Fishing is undoubtedly one of the
more popular hobbies here in MineScape!

7a9dc31a-478b-4afa-9dde-8e03b2c63c38.title: Survival Expert
7a9dc31a-478b-4afa-9dde-8e03b2c63c38.text:
Whenever you see sparkling waters, you can be sure
there's probably some good fishing to be had there!

3537b0c5-5052-472a-b5bd-bfb67e9473b7.title: Survival Expert
3537b0c5-5052-472a-b5bd-bfb67e9473b7.text:
Not only are fish absolutely delicious when cooked, there
are always fighters willing to buy a well cooked
fish when they're low on health.

5fdfe6b2-8b1e-4c82-8b5f-7046ebedd3f6.title: Survival Expert
5fdfe6b2-8b1e-4c82-8b5f-7046ebedd3f6.text:
I would recommend everybody has a go at Fishing at
least once in their lives! Was there anything else you
wished to hear again?

abfdb8ed-3f73-49dd-9ad2-a998d9918fac.title: <player>
abfdb8ed-3f73-49dd-9ad2-a998d9918fac.text: Tell me about my stats again.

95d7bb03-8240-4856-a241-50e1e4d8cd10.title: Survival Expert
95d7bb03-8240-4856-a241-50e1e4d8cd10.text:
Yas, the most basic of survival techniques. Most simple
meals can be cooked on a fire by right clicking on the
fire, then left clicking on the food.

0eaa775e-90bc-40a6-96c1-ba739d4c3814.title: Survival Expert
0eaa775e-90bc-40a6-96c1-ba739d4c3814.text:
Eating food will restore a little health. The harder
something is to cook, the more it will heal you.
Somewhere around here is a chef who will tell you more
about food and cooking it.

a5b19b47-b36b-47db-8eee-735cf45e4e61.title: Survival Expert
a5b19b47-b36b-47db-8eee-735cf45e4e61.text:
To look at your own stats, click on the bar graph icon found
in your backpack. In this panel you can check
your skill level.

7b7fd009-c86a-4910-a810-d39bcbbe7d18.title: Survival Expert
7b7fd009-c86a-4910-a810-d39bcbbe7d18.text:
As you move your mouse over any of the icons in this
panel, the small popup will show you the exact
amount of experience you have and how much is
needed to get to the next level.
